Rihana will be a good mum, his father has stated over her pregnancy. The “Shine Bright Like a Diamond” hitmaker announced that she’s pregnant and expecting her first baby with boyfriend A$AP Rocky on Monday. The couple shared the joyful news by releasing a photoshoot in which Barbadian singer is seen with her baby bump on display for the first time.   My father wanted me to study Law — Comedian Oga Sabinus     Don’t be like me, Tonto Dikeh advises fans     Kenneth Okonkwo commends lady for accepting proposal on knee   The singer’s father in a statement expressed absolute joy about the expected addition to his family. - Advertisement - “I’m so happy that I jumped for joy. I’m still so excited,” he said. Predicting what motherhood will be like for the singer, Ronald said: “Rihanna always said that she wanted children, she loves kids. She always takes care of her cousins’ kids…she’s going to be a good mum.” The soon-to-be-granddad who seemed impressed with Rocky gave the rapper his seal of approval as he described him as a ‘cool guy’, maintaining that he liked him. Fenty met A$AP Rocky when the daughter brought him home to their home in Caribbean Island in December 2020.